{"tid":318484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：3張總成本估計約85,000元新歇腳櫈得單座位　街坊點傾偈？","createTime":"2017-07-12T06:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T00:36:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a04e372614dc0ee5039430f2d7de994be40bda6b","tid":318484,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"07月11日(二) 18:02<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170711/photo/bkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170711183927\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170711183927&h=614d4687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社區設施好壞影響市民的生活質素，有網民今日在Facebook群組「西環變幻時」中上載圖片，指出西環山市街的斜路新建椅子工程已經竣工，新建有3張總成本估計約85,000元的單座位歇腳櫈讓街坊休憩。然而有街坊發現，有別舊櫈有雙座位設計，每張獨立裝設的歇腳櫈相隔甚遠又沒有上蓋，加上椅子下建有基座，擔心會絆倒老人家，令人質疑櫈子的實用性及價值。<br />\n<br />\n「山市街新座椅裝好咗喇！ 」網民Fio Fion Fiona&lrm;今日在Facebook群組上載3張社區內新建歇腳櫈的相片，分享工程已竣工。該批櫈子屬山市街座椅重置工程，經2016年中西區地區小型工程計劃撥款興建，當時總工程預算約為85,000元，即每張座椅成本約為28,000元。<br />\n<br />\n網民看見此新椅後都議論紛紛。先是選址方面，有人認為不應建在沒遮蔭的地方：「日曬雨淋邊個會坐」；有人則覺得單座位不利街坊聊天，而最令人憂慮的是椅子下的台階，網民擔心台階會絆倒老人家。其次價錢亦是討論的重點，有網民認為工程貴得不合理，但有人亦試圖為工程成本解畫：「地底可能有管道線管等，要升高一些。公平一些天氣有熱有涼，不能滿足每一個人眼球需要。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170711/bkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170711%2Fbkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001.html&d=824RU93fzWklzC%2BX%2F3vUCQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f1d34f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170711/bkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8c57f6c26f218c81bddae6ac364fbae8687d4265","tid":318484,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"岩我依啲毒撚"},{"pid":"0ef1e6f16d03bd1f071c9bcb93a17f71dbad2a01","tid":318484,"uid":45232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"唔好質疑廢老既聲量"},{"pid":"047521e5b837427215ed751eaf6fcbdaf5415d11","tid":318484,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"毒撚位"},{"pid":"5c343da58e85c5071bc5549d0c67f140f390c2af","tid":318484,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b879026c374b2f760fd189018aa1815b5cbc5444","tid":318484,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b5b46f3a4019c3ea77569284629632c2ba42c9d","tid":318484,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"石屎唔洗錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955cfa2569f14b0d3fd9fbb5e3b094bf748e0921","tid":318484,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"下面個躉係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15929e5a0f65f844d284a04222ea60d9794a3c16","tid":318484,"uid":15793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下面個躉係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在台上我覓理想"},{"pid":"fa37f646e98b5c5a44bee0a0458f190e092668e8","tid":318484,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下面個躉係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n市區骨位嚟"},{"pid":"a87fea084e80d636bbd37cce70470b7f2751d74b","tid":318484,"uid":65578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"政府批得出呢啲項目真係⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話無人有貪/利益我真係唔撚信"},{"pid":"608248ddcc148b6336e9ed910051fdfde5e0436d","tid":318484,"uid":15120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾盡咪2000蚊整到，20000買張咁既垃圾仲信香港冇貪污咩"},{"pid":"19de3622b8e9e830485d92c63c261d58dd760a53","tid":318484,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾盡咪2000蚊整到，20000買張咁既垃圾仲信香港冇貪污咩</blockquote><br />\n你又誇張左...你做到我俾夠5000 你幫整張"},{"pid":"d1c151f49c14764c56ef061a4a4a320eeb35292f","tid":318484,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"西環果個垃圾維穩群組黎<br />\n我女朋友比人踢左出去<br />\n表面上係黃絲開<br />\n但係入面就充滿藍絲係入面洗版<br />\n每一日都係班廢老廢中飲飲食食， 撚貓， 賣廣告<br />\n每到有重要議題， 就會有人洗版<br />\n用最低質不停一個回覆放一張相<br />\n我見過有後生你屌鳩過班廢老<br />\n但係反比成班人圍返轉頭"},{"pid":"c859d5f36fa2b7c07fbfdc26274f2121ab59f363","tid":318484,"uid":28367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:44:51.000Z","msg":"每張櫈分開計來做計<br />\n<br />\n1. 單座位櫈：2000/張<br />\n2. 基躉材料：2000/個<br />\n3. 監督管理：5000/張<br />\n4. 工人薪金：1500/日/人<br />\n<br />\n以一張櫈要3日，每日2工人來完成=9000/張<br />\n<br />\n每張都係：2000+2000+5000+9000=18,000<br />\n<br />\n鳩估之下，成單至少賺31,000<br />\n<br />\n接到呢啲工程真係第四、五判都有錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a9329d82b0816de617af8089684079d17adbea","tid":318484,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚位</blockquote><br />\n高左一級<br />\n毒撚坐好驚俾人望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18bbc908d7fc2b405beb112c544e563899b2f24","tid":318484,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"放三張天王椅會唔會平啲呢"},{"pid":"a2ed57dd3a49dda48efb6f26576edc77a963acf1","tid":318484,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"冇所謂嘅， 班廢老明明面對面傾偈都可以嗌破喉嚨咁嘅聲量， 少擔心啦"},{"pid":"3cb01caa702e42ec01cd390ac719cc604d85242a","tid":318484,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462a6f27aec54d59e8ac46b7c8c888f9e92ca9a9","tid":318484,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<br />\n高官連三張櫈都整唔到賺仲多啦"},{"pid":"6d32b0600a419b0491d5b0604d19e511d1e2afb1","tid":318484,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}